{
 "name": "RPlog_Joir_and_Adlerson",
 "title": "Joir and Adlerson",
 "summary": "In a private back office of the Imperial embassy on Caspar, Vice Director Joir of the Bureau of Operations meets Grand Admiral Adlerson, his cold composure betraying a rare hint of worry. Joir reports troubling intelligence -- gathered through the mercenary informant McTavish -- that Caspar is going on alert over a likely civil war within the Empire, possibly emanating from the OS Redemption system. Probing each other carefully, the two realize neither is part of any plot, and Adlerson reveals he has been quietly using McTavish, Ambassador Pantek, and others to investigate the brewing treason. They agree on a course of feigned ignorance -- letting Troy and McTavish play hero -- while they work to root out the threat, and Joir pledges his unwavering support to the Empire.",
